item.title: About Me
item.description: Håfa adai! Guahu si David Taitingfong — welcome to my blog. Here’s a list about me. I: am Chamoru with roots in Guahan am a software dev — I 💚 Python love coffee ☕ (blonde roasts!) love hiking 🥾 love gaming 🎮 — which is probably what got me into coding like tequila 🥃 (blancos ftw) like beer 🍻 (stouts & porters plz) Updated as of 2020-10-25.
